please startgame.py to luanch the game
before start the game , please ensure your python version higher than 3.9.0
please enter 'win+r' -> 'cmd' to the terminal.then enter 'pip instsall pygame' and 'pip instsall Tk'
!attention! this game have unseekable bug in json file loading it different from user you can restart game to repair it
====================================================================================================
请使用startgame.py来驱动游戏
再驱动游戏之前， 请确保你的python版本是3.9.0或以上
然后输入 'win+r' -> 'cmd' 打开运行窗，分别输入'pip instsall pygame'和'pip instsall Tk'
！警告！ 此游戏的json档案可能会在写出时报错，重开游戏便可解决